'''Cirlce 15''' was a landing pad in [[Rintatta City]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Exocron]]. [[Talon Karrde]] and his group of [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] landed at Circle 15 when going to Exocron to visit [[Jorj Car'das]].

